place.name: MARNOCH
place.gazetteerText: Marnoch, par., in NE. of Banff shire, 14,954 ac., pop. 3230; P.O., at Bridge of Marnoch, on river Deveron, 2 miles SW. of Aberchirder. (In 1887, John Bartholomew's Gazetteer of the British Isles)
